{"tid":2426383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"樓上唱卡拉ok嘈撚柒住哂可以點算","createTime":"2021-02-28T05:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T05:56:21.000Z","uid":304447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a43eb4fcdc8a534adba04bc61f60b6eb4e251bfb","tid":2426383,"uid":304447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:22:40.000Z","msg":"話說我樓上住咗個中坑，條友同佢個男人婆女朋友心血來潮就鍾意唱k，個音響播到成幢屋都聽到。<br />\n<br />\n我間房咁啱就對正喺佢哋間k房下面，朝早唱，半夜又唱，我成日唔係俾佢哋嘈醒，就係俾佢哋搞到失眠，真係好撚辛苦呀。<br />\n<br />\n屋企人試過見面嗰陣提佢哋唱歌好大聲；我自己亦都試過襯佢唱到一半等伴奏嗰陣開窗屌佢哋，但係停咗兩日又故態復萌，仲好似同我示威咁大聲咗。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋而家又唱緊喇，想知有咩辦法可以令佢哋收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c7e4cd726682a1a74df9a81e307dd0bbc1ab37","tid":2426383,"uid":18001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"一陣投訴俾人話你破壞音樂文化<br />\n幫差佬執法"},{"pid":"f9575df4212b03ed5310c5177028aa21c50ebc4a","tid":2426383,"uid":201656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"報狗話樓上唱願榮光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />包佢即刻收皮"},{"pid":"2fe43c40e8d5f72478e3d8f977b623857c8c525c","tid":2426383,"uid":304447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9575df4212b03ed5310c5177028aa21c50ebc4a","tid":2426383,"uid":201656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"報狗話樓上唱願榮光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />包佢即刻收皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:30:27.000Z","msg":"報狗驚搞埋我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8289072afc84ba39a0def228cd3b0e695666c86","tid":2426383,"uid":283903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:41:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f113fcdddd63a8d9cf93d19f8cfcaef002721fec","tid":2426383,"uid":304447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:56